title: C. Array Sum
statement: You are given an array of integers. Calculate the sum of its elements.
inputSpecification: The i-th line of the input contains an integer ai (0 ≤ a ≤ 1000) — the i-th element of the array. The size of the array is between 1 and 10, inclusive. Note that the size of the array is not given explicitly!
outputSpecification: Output a single integer — the sum of the elements of the array.
name: Array Sum
